data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
This little tool assists you with Uru Live-created JPEG images (such as KI images or portraits of your avatar).
A bug currently in Uru Live causes such images to be created with a slightly corrupt format, preventing many image viewers and editors from opening them properly. This tool remedies that problem on particular images.
Do not apply this tool on non-JPEG images or any other files, especially not in Overwrite mode.
